'''Consolidated Shipping''' was a transport business that was large enough to be granted some autonomy by the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. Based in the [[Shelsha sector/Legends|Shelsha sector]], it was represented by a star-in-swirl shape logo. It had a hub on [[Drunost]].

